## Key Features

* Real-time Linux server monitoring
* CPU, Memory, Disk, and Network visibility
* Prometheus-based metric collection
* Grafana dashboard visualization
* Alertmanager integration
* Slack-based incident notifications
* Production-style troubleshooting and Root Cause Analysis (RCA)
* Infrastructure observability implementation

